
Included on this disk are the following files

CONTENTS               - This contents file
1p_levels              - 1 player levels directory
2p_levels              - 2 player levels directory
BeBop_sounds           - BeBop digitized sounds and intro music directory
Boards                 - directory containing game boards
Board_patterns         - directory of board background graphics
libs                   - contains iff.library support graphics library
Pieces                 - contains different piece shape sets
puzzles                - directory with graphical puzzle images
s                      - contains startup-sequence 
Saved_Games            - directory for up to 8 saved game positions
BeBop Demo             - Main code for BeBop 'N Drop Demo program
BeBop Demo.info        - Icon for BeBop Demo
blitter_piece_images   - Graphics for piece sets
Help_Screen            - Keyboard key definitions, etc.
MAKE_BOOTABLE          - Script for installing game to boot under Dos 1.3
makebootscript         - " "
MAKE_BOOTABLE2.0       - Script for installing game to boot under Dos 2.0
makebootscript2.0      - " "
QUICK_INSTALL          - Program to copy necessary iff.library to libs: dir
startup_picture        - Title Screen
team_picture           - Group photo of developers
top_ten_scores         - Storage of top ten game scores
